(91, 42, '<h2>Positive Reinforcement backed by experts.\r\nMeet our Pet Wellness Council</h2>', '2021-09-05 02:57:06', '2021-09-04 23:58:16'),
(92, 3, '<h2>Tips and tricks for maintaining your pet\'s health between salon visits</h2>', '2021-09-09 08:12:07', '2021-09-09 02:50:21'),
(93, 3, '<h4>Dog Grooming</h4><h4>\r\n<p>MPMP is the pet grooming destination for all of your pet’s needs. Our full-service cat and dog grooming provide premier care for your pet. Our certified groomers are with your dog or cat every step of the way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With over 800 hours of hands-on grooming instruction over a 20-week course, our passionate groomers provide the best care for your dog or cat. Helping your pet look and feel their best, our groomers are trained to provide a 7-point pet care check to provide a health check between regular veterinary visits. The 7-point pet care check should never replace regular veterinary visits.</p>\r\n\r\n</h4><h4>Cat Grooming</h4>\r\n<p>Cat grooming services are available at select locations. Contact your neighborhood Petco store to confirm availability of a cat groomer. We help your cat look and feel great with a refreshing grooming appointment.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Dog And Puppy Grooming</h4>\r\n<p>Our full-service dog grooming services help dogs look and feel their best. Dog grooming services include brushing, nail-trimming and buffing, bathing, cut and style, gland expression and more. Petco dog groomers provide breed-specific haircuts and baths. Upgrade your dog’s grooming visit with customizable packages designed for specific needs–de-shedding, sensitive skin care and more. Add on teeth-brushing to your visit as part of a regular dental care routine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Book an appointment for dog grooming near you today. Whether your pup is needing a full-service groom or one of our a lá carte services such as dog nail-trimming, our certified dog groomers are passionate about what they do in helping your pet look and feel their best.</p>', '2021-09-09 08:28:04', '2021-09-09 03:00:16');
