(13, '1627486589.jpg', 'Cuddler Mink', 'Provides comfort & security for anxious pets!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Australian Made Cuddler in luxurious Dune is the perfect bed to calm and relax your pet. Super soft long pile vegan faux fur paired with soft raised walls and a deep sleeping area provide the ultimate retreat for anxious pets and those that relish the feeling of safety and security. The Dune Cuddler invites hours of delicious snoozing and is fully machine washable (even the filling!).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features removable, replaceable and washable covers on both the outer ring and cushion. Filled with Snoozafill, our Australian Foam and recycled PET fibre mix, zippered access to the inner liners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '1', '1', '1628110276.jpg', '1628110287.jpg', '1627487430.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', 'X-Large', NULL, NULL, 119.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-15 15:17:38', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm).', 'All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove covers before washing. We recommend closing all zips and making use of a laundry bag to protect the long fibres.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p></p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>\r\n<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-18 14:59:00', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cuddler-mink'),
(14, '1626346883.jpg', 'The Supa Snooza', NULL, 1, '1', '<p>Our all-new Supa Snooza TUFF is built extremely strong and durable. Abrasion and scratch proof with high performance and waterproof 1680 Denier fabric to handle Aussie conditions. The soft high walled water-resistant all-weather outer shell cocoons your pet providing protection from wind, while a plush deep sleeping area provides comfort and security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The reversible cushion has the option of plush on one side and Tuff 1680 denier fabric on the other, handling muddy paws &amp; soggy dogs with ease. A breeze to keep clean the SnoozaTUFF Supa Snooza can be wiped down easily and is also machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stuffed full of recycled PET fibre, the TUFF SUPA Snooza is not only fabulous for your pet but good for the planet too – now that’s SUPA!</p>', '2', NULL, '1626346850.jpg', '1627494100.jpg', '1627494111.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', 'X-Large', NULL, NULL, 139.9, 179.9, 179.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-15 17:00:50', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>\r\n<p>Boston Terrier photographed in Medium Size</p>\r\n<p>Mini Groodle photographed in Large Size</p>\r\n<p>Boxer/American Bulldog pictured in Extra Large Size</p>', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '-', '-', NULL, NULL, NULL, '650', '520', NULL, NULL, NULL, '850', '710', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1000', '840', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>SUPA simple to clean the body responds extremely well to a simple wipe down, however for a deeper clean and if the size of your machine allows it can be machine washed too. The removable and reversible plush cushion is fully machine washable. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w86eYtWExB8\" target=\"_blank\">Watch the video</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Cushion &amp; Body</strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Recycled PET Fill</p>', '2021-08-07 23:56:59', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'the-supa-snooza'),
(17, '1626367993.jpg', 'Cuddler Charcoal', 'Provides comfort & security for anxious pets!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Australian Made Cuddler in luxurious Charcoal is the perfect bed to calm and relax your pet. Super soft long pile vegan faux fur paired with soft raised walls and a deep sleeping area provide the ultimate retreat for anxious pets and those that relish the feeling of safety and security. The Charcoal Cuddler invites hours of delicious snoozing and is fully machine washable (even the filling!).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features removable, replaceable and washable covers on both the outer ring and cushion. Filled with Snoozafill, our Australian Foam and recycled PET fibre mix, zippered access to the inner liners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '1', '1', '1628110369.jpg', '1628110379.jpg', '1626368076.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'X-Large', NULL, 99.9, 119.9, 229.9, 189.9, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-15 22:53:13', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', 'All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing. We recommend closing all zips and making use of a laundry bag to protect the long fibres.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling : </strong>\r\nWarm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-10 17:22:12', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cuddler-charcoal'),
(22, '1626373130.jpg', 'The Cat Bed Chinchilla', 'Convertible & reversible - use 3 ways!', 2, '44', '<p>Designed for the quarantine services of Australia for use in their feline facility. The brief was big… with washability (for obvious reasons) & durability being most important of all.</p> \r\n<p>The Cat Bed is a favourite, as it can be inverted, reversed & converted & is fully machine washable & extra durable. It’s made using luxurious faux fur, offering two pile heights. The opening has flexible boning to keep it open or rolled down as you please.\r\n</p>\r\n<p> Use this bed in its tunnel form with the plush fur inside or out, rolled into a pod or turn it into a cuddly round bed. This ultimate cat bed is also great for small dogs, rabbits, guinea pigs, ferrets & rats. This cat bed is also covered by the Snooza Repair Service.</p>', '116', '42', '1626373174.jpg', '1626373256.jpg', '1626373285.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 69.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-16 00:18:50', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate</p>', 'Diameter', 'Length', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '360', '460', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>\r\n<p>Polyester</p>', '2021-10-08 16:24:16', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'the-cat-bed-chinchilla'),
(24, '1626374094.jpg', 'Cat Cocoon Grey', 'The perfect undercover snuggle spot.', 2, '51', '<p>Our new Cat Cocoon in grey is the perfect undercover snuggle spot for those that like to burrow and hide. Finished in grey mock suede (made from upholstery grade fabric which is wrinkle & hair resistant) the interior burrow is lined with the softest grey plush faux fur to provide absolute comfort.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOur new one-piece cover design has a removable formed hoop that gives height to the entry making it the ideal bed to snuggle into and non-slip paws on the base make it the perfect bed for wooden or tiled floors.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOur new Cocoon has a one-piece removable zippered cover meaning washing is a cinch and zippered access to the soft filled insert means you can top it up over time, or customise the level of fill to your liking.</p>', '4', '26', '1626374149.jpg', '1626374232.jpg', '1626374232.jpg', 'Small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 169.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-16 00:34:54', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover &amp; boning from the hood.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cushion Insert (with fill)</strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p><strong>Faux Fur / Faux Suede (Polyester)</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Filled with Snoozafill*</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Made with Australian Foam</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-08 16:31:59', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cat-cocoon-grey'),
(25, '1626374444.jpg', 'Travel Bed', NULL, 1, '8', '<p>This stylish Travel Bed is perfect for nervous travellers, calming them with a comfortable, familiar space of their own whilst travelling in the car. It has a dual function - both a travel bed in the car and a portable bed for use at your destination, eg. outdoors or on vacation.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe padded walls and calming plush cushion make a cosy, comforting space for your dog. The cushion is reversible, with chinchilla faux-fur or water-resistant sides to choose from depending on the need. The bed body is made from good quality high-density polyester which is water-resistant and tear-resistant while protecting your car seats.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nThe Travel Bed features two adjustable, positional straps to hold the chair in place. The back strap loops around the car chair and the top strap loops around the headrest.\r\nThe medium size has two elastic tabs & hooks at lower back corners, to tether with car seat anchor points.\r\nThe cushion is removable and machine washable. Spot cleaning recommended for the main bed body.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n*IMPORTANT: Please note this Snooza travel bed is not a safety device. Dog should be attached by a harness to the seatbelt for the safety of the animal and the driver.</p>', '13', NULL, '1626374522.jpg', '1626374575.jpg', '1626374618.jpg', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 139.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-16 00:40:44', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2021-07-16 00:43:38', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'travel-bed'),
(26, '1626375377.jpg', 'Out N About Natural', 'Comfort in the cargo area with a topped & water resistant bed!', 1, '8', '<p>Designed to fit most wagons &amp; 4wds the Out \'n\' About® bed is the ideal way to travel in style. Plus it keeps your car nice &amp; clean! The mat insert is removable &amp; reversible. A woolly side for a snugglier ride &amp; a super tough, water resistant, 600 denier ripstop side for sandy trips to the beach &amp; muddy walks. The outer also works just as well on its own as a protective lining for the cargo area. The mat &amp; outer covers are fully washable, including removable, washable bolster inserts, but with the fabulous PU coated fabric you may never need to, just the occasional spot clean.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nFinally arrive at your destination &amp; this bed is easily removed to become a great place to rest whilst on holiday, camping sleep-overs...</p>', '13', NULL, '1626375506.jpg', '1626375533.jpg', '', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 259.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-16 00:56:17', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', 'All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '1000', '1000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>Polyester Mock Lambswool</p>\r\n<p>Polyester Rip Stop Fabric</p>', '2021-07-28 17:52:29', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'out-n-about-natural'),
(28, '1627381676.png', 'Fleaproofer Dog Bed - Green', NULL, 1, '1', '<p>Australian made by us, the Fleaproofer sits 20cm above the ground and features the Snooza Original Dog Bed frame with a shade cloth type cover that the fleas will just hate to live in! With 2 velcro tabs to hold it in place & ultra high-tech UV treated thread & fabric, the cover is perfect for outdoor conditions. Made to suit those customers who had an Original Dog Bed but wanted a \'Flea-Free\' style cover - now you can.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nOur Fleaproofer frame can also be used withour Original Dog Bed covers as well as our many accessories - Woolly Covers, Multimats.</p>', '2', '31', '1627381417.png', '1627381636.png', NULL, 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, 89.9, 99.9, 109.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-27 16:17:45', 'Sleeping area. All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', 'All sizes are approximate. For overall length of the bed (including the legs) add approximately 20cm.', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '690', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '900', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1020', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1150', '780', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', 'Remove the cover. Wash with a mix of 1/4 cup bleach, 1/4 cup of mild detergent & 4 litres of water. Do not use solvent based cleaners. Line dry only', 'Synthetic Cover,Australian Steel', '2021-10-11 05:49:55', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'fleaproofer-dog-bed-green'),
(29, '1627407098.jpg', 'Cocoon - Grey', 'The perfect undercover snuggle spot.', 1, '1', '<p><strong>The Cocoon - Grey</strong></p> \r\n<p>Snooza NEW Cocoon in grey is the perfect undercover snuggle spot for those that like to burrow and hide. Finished in grey mock suede (made from upholstery grade fabric which is wrinkle &amp; hair resistant) the interior burrow is lined with the softest grey plush faux fur to provide absolute comfort.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n new one-piece cover design has a removable formed hoop that gives height to the entry making it the ideal bed to snuggle into and non-slip paws on the base make it the perfect bed for wooden or tiled floors.</p>\r\n<p>\r\nnew Cocoon has a one-piece removable zippered cover meaning washing is a cinch and zippered access to the soft filled insert means you can top it up over time, or customise the level of fill to your liking.</p>', '1', '7', '1627407128.jpg', '1627407150.jpg', '1627407192.jpg', 'Small', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 169.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-27 23:31:38', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', 'All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.\r\nBoston Terrier photographed in Small Size', 'Diameter', 'Gusset Height', 'Hood Opening', NULL, NULL, NULL, '650', '120', '400', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '850', '160', '650', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover &amp; boning from the hood.</p><p><b>Cover :&nbsp;</b><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</span></p><p><b>Cushion Insert (with fill) :&nbsp;</b><span>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</span></p>', '<p>1. Faux Fur / Faux Suede (Polyester)</p><p>2. Filled with Snoozafill</p><p>3. Made with Australian Foam,Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-11 05:47:54', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cocoon-grey'),
(30, '1627417111.jpg', 'Sudz Budz', 'The perfect accessory for your dog\'s laundry!', 1, '7', '<p>Here at Snooza we love anything multi-purpose, the more things you can do with something the better! Sudz Budz are the felted wool balls that do it all (well perhaps not all... but they do a fair bit and they\'re environmentally friendly!). Sudz Budz are the perfect washing &amp; drying accessory for your pet\'s laundry - and they can also be used as a toy (under supervision of course)! Perfect for aerating and reviving lofty products such as pet bedding, cushions, pillows and other soft filled items.&nbsp;</p><p>Each pack of Sudz Budz contains 6 felted wool balls.</p><p>They are chemical-free, hypoallergenic, compostable, biodegradable are a natural fabric softener and can help reduce drying time when using a dryer.</p>', '12', NULL, '1627418010.jpg', '1627418082.jpg', NULL, 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 27.95, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 02:18:31', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '6 balls per pack', 'Diameter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '80', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p><b>In the wash and dryer:</b></p><p>Toss 4 - 6 Sudz Budz in the wash with your pet\'s bed covers to help gently remove ingrained dirt &amp; hair and then pop them in the dryer to realise the natural fabric softening action and hair attracting qualities of the felted balls.</p>\r\n<p><b>To revive your Snoozafill:</b></p>\r\n<p>Placing one or two Sudz Budz inside your Snooza calico cover or laundry bag with your Snoozafill when washing and drying will help revive the fill and add more loft to your pet\'s bedding.</p>\r\n<p>(Be sure to refer to washing instructions on your Snooza product).</p>', '<p>Hand felted organic wool<br></p>', '2021-07-28 02:45:24', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'sudz-budz'),
(31, '1627419123.jpg', 'Ropee', 'Tug it, toss it, fetch it or catch it!', 1, '7', '<p>Lightweight &amp; easy to handle the Ropee© can be used frisbee style or as a tuggy. It\'s great at the beach &amp; just like our beds it\'s fully washable, very fitting for a dog toy. No squeaky noises or obnoxiously funny shapes but we like it that way.</p>', '12', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 12.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 02:52:03', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Diameter', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '200', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<ul class=\"arham\">\r\n<li>Polyester Rope</li>\r\n<li>Cotton</li>\r\n</ul>', '2021-07-28 03:18:56', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'ropee'),
(33, '1627470496.jpg', 'Calming Multimat Silver Fox', 'Fully washable go-anywhere calming mat; perfect for crate, floor, car & home.', 1, '1', '<p>Snooza Australian Made Calming Mulitmat is the perfect all-round versatile Mat. Featuring the same material as Snooza  Calming Cuddler beds the Calming Multimat® was designed to snuggly fit all popular crate sizes. Using some of the same principles as the cuddler, the texture of the soft long pile faux fur helps to calm pets allowing them to snuggle into the fibres - perfect to help anxious pets. It\'s a fantastic go-anywhere multi-purpose mat - it makes a super floor mat, crate mat, puppy training mat, in the car or on holiday.</p>\r\n<p>Made in Melbourne, thick wadding is encased in the long pile plush and then notched to keep it in place. We\'ve added velcro tabs at each corner to fit all Snooza Raised Bed (to stop it sliding around), and because it\'s a \'ridgy-didge\' Australian Made Snooza Multimat® it is fully machine washable.</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking to use your Calming Multimat on one of Snooza raised beds, the sizes are one size down i.e. a medium size Multimat will fit a Small size Original Dog Bed, Fleaproofer or Flea-Free Dog Bed, a large-size Multimat will fit a medium raised bed etc.</p>\r\n<p>Please note: The sizing on our multimats varies between the Choc/Sand Polar Fleece Multimat &amp; the Chinchilla and Calming Multimats. The Chinchilla &amp; Calming Multimats are designed to fit the most popular crate sizes as well as our raised beds.</p>', '1', '69', '1627471109.jpg', '1627471134.jpg', '1627471171.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'X-Large', 'XX-Large', 69.9, 79.9, 89.9, 99.9, 109.9, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 17:08:16', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', 'Please note: The sizing on the Choc/Sand Multimat differs to that on the Chinchilla Multimat.', 'Length', 'Width', 'Crate Size', 'Snooza Raised Bed Size', NULL, 'Small', '610', '430', '24\'\'', '-', NULL, '780', '520', '30\'\'', 'S', NULL, '910', '600', '36\'\'', 'M', NULL, '1090', '720', '42\'\'', 'L', NULL, '1220', '760', '48\'\'', 'XL', NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', 'true', '<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>•	Polyester</p>\r\n<p>•	Made with Recycled PET Wadding</p>', '2021-10-18 14:58:37', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'calming-multimat-silver-fox'),
(34, '1627472207.jpg', 'Multimat', 'Reversible, fully washable go-anywhere mat!', 1, '1', '<p>Snooza Australian Made Calming Mulitmat is the perfect all-round versatile Mat. Featuring the same material as Snooza  Calming Cuddler beds the Calming Multimat® was designed to snuggly fit all popular crate sizes. Using some of the same principles as the cuddler, the texture of the soft long pile faux fur helps to calm pets allowing them to snuggle into the fibres - perfect to help anxious pets. It\'s a fantastic go-anywhere multi-purpose mat - it makes a super floor mat, crate mat, puppy training mat, in the car or on holiday.</p>\r\n<p>Made in Melbourne, thick wadding is encased in the long pile plush and then notched to keep it in place. We\'ve added velcro tabs at each corner to fit all Snooza Raised Bed (to stop it sliding around), and because it\'s a \'ridgy-didge\' Australian Made Snooza Multimat® it is fully machine washable.</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking to use your Calming Multimat on one of Snooza raised beds, the sizes are one size down i.e. a medium size Multimat will fit a Small size Original Dog Bed, Fleaproofer or Flea-Free Dog Bed, a large-size Multimat will fit a medium raised bed etc.</p>\r\n<p>Please note: The sizing on our multimats varies between the Choc/Sand Polar Fleece Multimat &amp; the Chinchilla and Calming Multimats. The Chinchilla &amp; Calming Multimats are designed to fit the most popular crate sizes as well as our raised beds.</p>', '1', '69', '1627472230.jpg', '1627472255.jpg', '1627472278.jpg', 'Large', 'X-Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 79.9, 89.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 17:32:37', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm).', 'Please note: The sizing on the Choc/Sand Multimat differs to that on the Chinchilla Multimat.All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, '