(35, '1627481469.jpg', 'SupaDry Noodle Mat Storm', 'Perfect to keep at the door, for bath time or in the car!', 1, '1', '<p>The Supa Dry Mat soaks up water to keep wet pawprints off your floor! The perfect addition to your grooming routine, the two-tone high pile super soft microfibre noodles soak up to 8X their weight in water and will hold more water than any ordinary towel! Perfect to have at the door to wipe wet, muddy paws before they run through the house, to use at bathtime or keep one in the back of the car.</p>', '2', NULL, '1627481498.jpg', '1627481514.jpg', NULL, 'One Size', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 69.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 20:11:09', 'One size - 900m x 600mm.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Machine wash on 40 Degree cycle.</p>', '<p>Polyester</p>', '2021-07-28 20:13:08', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'supaDry-noodle-mat-storm'),
(36, '1627481745.jpg', 'SupaDry Noodle Mat Zinc', 'Perfect to keep at the door, for bath time or in the car!', 1, '1', '<p>The Supa Dry Mat soaks up water to keep wet pawprints off your floor! The perfect addition to your grooming routine, the grey two-tone high pile super soft microfibre noodles soak up to 8X their weight in water and will hold more water than any ordinary towel! With a size of 900mm x 600mm, it\'s perfect to have at the door to wipe wet, muddy paws before they run through the house, to use at bathtime or keep one in the back of the car.</p>', '2', NULL, '1627481774.jpg', '1627481793.jpg', NULL, 'One Size', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 69.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 20:15:45', '•	One size - 900m x 600mm.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>•	Machine wash on 40 Degree cycle</p>', '<p>•	Polyester</p>', '2021-07-28 20:18:26', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'supaDry-noodle-mat-zinc'),
(37, '1627488328.jpg', 'Cuddler Chinchilla', 'Indulgently snuggly in the plushest charcoal faux fur!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Chinchilla range provides luxury, comfort and style complementing today’s modern décor while providing optimum comfort for your pet. The Australian Made Chinchilla cuddler invites hours of delicious snoozing for your pet to snuggle, cuddle, curl or stretch. Finished in the plushest grey-toned faux fur the soft outer walls protect and cocoon while the removable cushion is filled with just enough Snoozafill® for those pets who like to nest. Features non-slip base and removable and washable covers on both the outer ring and cushion. Zippered access to the Snoozafill* filled inners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>', '1', '1', '1628110447.jpg', '1628110461.jpg', '1627488412.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, 99.9, 119.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 22:05:28', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p><br></p>', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-16 19:24:08', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cuddler-chinchilla'),
(38, '1627489032.jpg', 'Cuddler Elk', 'Indulgently snuggly in soft golden brown toned faux fur!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Australian Made Cuddler in Elk invites hours of delicious snoozing for your pet to snuggle, cuddle, curl or stretch. Swathed in a longer pile golden brown toned faux fur the soft outer walls protect and cocoon while the removable cushion is filled with just enough Snoozafill® for those pets who like to nest. Zippered access to the Snoozafill* filled inners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>', '1', '1', '1628110555.jpg', '1627490191.jpg', '1628110569.jpg', 'Small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 80, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 22:17:12', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p><br></p>', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-11 05:17:56', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cuddler-elk'),
(39, '1627491908.jpg', 'Cuddler Leopard', 'Indulgently snuggly in the plush Leopard faux fur!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Australian Made Cuddler Leopard invites hours of delicious snoozing for your pet to snuggle, cuddle, curl or stretch. Soft plush faux fur in a classic Leopard pattern is a fun but stylish statement. The soft outer walls protect and cocoon while the removable cushion is filled with just enough Snoozafill® for those pets who like to nest. Features non-slip base and removable and washable covers (including the inner covers) on both the outer ring and cushion. Even the covers Zippered access to the Snoozafill* filled inners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>', '1', '1', '1628110712.jpg', '1628110724.jpg', '1627492038.jpg', 'Small', 'Large', 'X-Large', NULL, NULL, 99.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 23:05:08', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p><br></p>', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Filling : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p>Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p>Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and frien