(40, '1627494380.jpg', 'Snooza TUFF Supa Snooza', '1680 Denier TUFF High-Performance Waterproof Fabric!', 1, '1', '<p>Our all-new Supa Snooza TUFF is built extremely strong and durable. Abrasion and scratch proof with high performance and waterproof 1680 Denier fabric to handle Aussie conditions. The soft high walled water-resistant all-weather outer shell cocoons your pet providing protection from wind, while a plush deep sleeping area provides comfort and security.</p>\r\n<p>The reversible cushion has the option of plush on one side and Tuff 1680 denier fabric on the other, handling muddy paws &amp; soggy dogs with ease. A breeze to keep clean the SnoozaTUFF Supa Snooza can be wiped down easily and is also machine washable.</p>\r\n<p>Stuffed full of recycled PET fibre, the TUFF SUPA Snooza is not only fabulous for your pet but good for the planet too – now that’s SUPA!</p>', '2', NULL, '1627494420.jpg', '1627494445.jpg', '1627494467.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 97.9, 125.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-28 23:46:20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2021-07-28 23:47:47', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'snooza-tuff-supa-snooza'),
(41, '1627495661.jpg', 'Ortho Lounger Blue', 'Orthopaedic outdoor comfort!', 1, '1', '<p>Orthopaedic, water repellent &amp; super stylish - the Australian Made Ortho Lounger from Snooza ticks all the boxes for ultimate comfort and functionality. The low profile one-piece mattress is beautifully contoured allowing pets to ‘lounge’ comfortably while the gentle rises allow them to rest their heads to keep an eye on their surroundings. Great for the lounge room, patio or deck!</p>\r\n<p>The low profile nature of the Ortho Lounger makes it ideal for elderly pets or those pets that may have trouble getting on or off higher beds due to limited mobility while the specially corrugated foam distributes weight effectively taking pressure off sensitive areas while promoting airflow throughout the mattress.</p>\r\n<p>Finished in stylish deep blue with charcoal piping the water repellent cover is fully zippered to make washing a breeze. Available in Medium and Large sizes.</p>', '2', '16', '1627495720.jpg', '1627495773.jpg', '1627495796.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 139.9, 209.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-07-29 00:07:41', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>\r\n<p>Dog in image pictured on a Large Size.</p>', 'Length', 'Width', 'Lowest Point', 'Highest Point', NULL, 'Small', '--', '--', '--', '--', NULL, '850', '550', '70', '140', NULL, '1150', '750', '70', '150', NULL, '--', '--', '--', '--', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover before washing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Foam :</strong>Spot clean only.</p>', '<p>Polyester Cover</p>\r\n<p>Australian Orthopaedic Foam</p>', '2021-10-11 06:04:08', 50, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'ortho-lounger-blue'),
