te: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p><p>- Polyester&nbsp; covers</p><p>- Snoozafill* side bolsters</p><p>- Faux fur plush interior lining</p><p>- Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</p><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-08 16:28:16', 1000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cat-ortho-nestler-soho'),
(83, '1627804018.jpg', 'Cat Buddy Bed Chinchilla', 'Furnishing grade fabric walls and a super soft plush interior - bliss!', 2, '44', '<p><strong>Cat Buddy Bed Chinchilla</strong></p> \r\n<p>new Chinchilla Buddy Bed provides luxury, comfort and style complementing today’s modern decor. The exterior of the high walls are finished in stylish upholstery two-tone fabric while the inside and soft cushion top are swathed with the plushest dark grey toned faux fur to give your pet hours of blissful sleep. Features a lightweight foam body, non-slip base and zippered removable covers with replaceable, refillable and washable Snoozafill®* cushion insert.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>', '116', '38', '1627804062.jpg', '1627804074.jpg', '1627804085.jpg', 'Small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 99.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-01 13:46:58', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '500', '470', '530', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Covers</strong> : Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p> \r\n<p><strong>Cushion (fill)</strong> : Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p> \r\n<p><strong>Foam Body</strong> : Foam Body</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p> - Polyester Covers</p>\r\n<p> - Body - Australian