(84, '1627808799.jpg', 'Cat Buddy Bed NEW Oslo', 'Brushed velvet-like textured walls and a super soft plush interior - bliss!', 2, '44', '<p><strong>Cat Buddy Bed Oslo</strong></p> \r\n<p>Snooza  calming Buddy Bed in Oslo adds a touch of luxe to the modern home. The high walls are finished in stylish grey-toned textured brushed velvet-like fabric on the outside while the inside walls and soft cushion top are swathed with the plushest faux fur helping your pet feel safe and secure. Features a lightweight foam body, non-slip base and zippered removable covers with replaceable, refillable and washable Snoozafill®* cushion insert</p>', '116', '38', '1627808853.jpg', '1627808864.jpg', NULL, 'Small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 99.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-01 15:06:39', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, '500', '470', '530', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers</span>&nbsp;: Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion (fill)</span>&nbsp;: Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Body</span>&nbsp;: Foam Body</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p><p>- Polyester Covers</p><p>- Body - Australian Foam</p><p>- Cushion - Filled with Snoozafill®*</p><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-08 15:08:03', 1000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cat-buddy-bed-new-oslo'),
(86, '1627815152.jpg', 'Cat TUFF Supa Snooza Navy', '1650 Denier High-Density Performance Fabric Surround!', 2, '44', '<p><strong>Cat Supa Snooza in High-Density Performance Fabric</strong></p> \r\n<p>all-new Supa Snooza TUFF is built extremely strong and durable. Abrasion and scratch proof with high performance and waterproof 1680 Denier fabric to handle Aussie conditions. The soft high walled water-resistant all-weather outer shell cocoons your pet providing protection from wind, while a plush deep sleeping area provides comfort and security.</p>\r\n<p>The reversible cushion has the option of plush on one side and Tuff 1680 denier fabric on the other, handling muddy paws &amp; soggy dogs with ease. A breeze to keep clean the SnoozaTUFF Supa Snooza can be wiped down easily and is also machine washable.</p>\r\n<p>Stuffed full of recycled PET fibre, the TUFF SUPA Snooza is not only fabulous for your pet but good for the planet too – now that’s SUPA!</p>', '116', '50', '1627815201.jpg', '1627815215.jpg', NULL, 'Medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 139.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-01 16:52:32', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of sleeping area', NULL, 'One Size', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '550', '650', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>SUPA simple to clean the body responds extremely well to a simple wipe down, however for a deeper clean and if the size of your machine allows it can be machine washed too. The removable and reversible plush cushion is fully machine washable.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion &amp; Body</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>This bed is tough but not indestructible, please beware of four-legged motivated repeat offenders.</p><p>- Polyester Covers</p><p>- Recycled PET Fill</p>', '2021-10-08 16:43:14', 1000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 'cat-tuff-supa-snooza-navy'),
(87, '1627887192.jpg', 'Cat Tuff Supa Snooza Granite', '1650 Denier High-Density Performance Fabric Surround!', 2, '44', '<p><strong>Cat Supa Snooza - Supa stylish &amp; cosy! </strong></p> \r\n<p>With all the luxury and comfort you’d expect from an indoor bed, the SUPA Snooza makes the transition from your interior to your outdoor patio or deck and back again effortlessly and with style. The soft high walled water-resistant outer shell cocoons your pet providing protection from wind, while a plush deep sleeping area provides comfort and security. Stuffed full of recycled PET fibre, the SUPA Snooza is not only fabulous for your pet but good for the planet too – now that’s SUPA!</p>', '116', '50', '1627887882.jpg', '1627887901.jpg', NULL, 'Medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 139.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-02 12:53:12', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '550', '650', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>SUPA simple to clean the body responds extremely well to a simple wipe down, however for a deeper clean and if the size of your machine allows it can be machine washed too. The removable and reversible plush cushion is fully machine washable.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion &amp; Body</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>This bed is tough but not indestructible, please beware of four-legged motivated repeat offenders.</p><p>- Polyester Covers</p><p>- Recycled PET Fill</p>', '2021-10-08 16:42:51', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ca