(90, '1627895328.jpg', 'Cat Scratching Pole Grey Plain', 'No need to replace the pole, just replace the cover when worn!', 2, '44', '<p><strong> Cat Scratching Pole - Grey</strong></p> \r\n<p>Cat Scratcher proudly sports the Australian Made &amp; Owned logo. There are many cat scratchers on the market but we think our one of a kind cat pole is the best cat scratcher around, you won\'t find anything like this anywhere!</p>\r\n<p>cat pole is made from Australian Made environmentally sustainable materials that attach firmly to a completely covered base. The Australian Made grey cover is cut &amp; sewn by Melbourne Snooza workshop. Instead of throwing the pole away once your cat has clawed through the fabric, we offer replacement covers. Staple free - simply slip the cover over the pole &amp; with different colours to choose from you\'ll never get tired of looking at it.</p>\r\n<p>Every component part of our cat scratching poles is fully recyclable.</p>', '116', '43', '1627895384.jpg', '1627895394.jpg', '1627895417.jpg', 'Small', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 89.9, 99.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-02 15:08:48', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Height', 'Diameter', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '520', '80', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '720', '80', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p><strong>Cover</strong></p> \r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Base</strong></p> \r\n<p>Sponge clean only.</p>', '<p> - Australian made Organic Timber encased in recycled plastic</p>\r\n<p> - Particleboard base</p>\r\n<p> - Australian Made Polyester Cover</p>', '2021-10-08 16:36:16', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'cat-scratching-pole-grey-plain'),
