(95, '1627899309.jpg', 'Cat Scratching Pole Cover Grey Plain', 'No need to replace the pole, just replace the cover when worn!', 7, '40', '<p>Snooza cat scratching pole covers are proudly made here in Australia</p><p>he great thing about our cat scratching poles is you can change your cover as you need or please! Simply slip the old worn cover off and slip on a new one - easy! Even better, cat pole covers are fully washable.</p><p>***The material for our cat scratching pole covers is made right here in Australia and we cut and sew the covers in our Melbourne factory!</p>', '84', '72', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 34.9, 39.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-02 16:15:09', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cover</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Base</span></p><p>Sponge clean only.</p>', '<p>- Polyester Cover<br></p>', '2021-10-11 07:48:43', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'cat-scratching-pole-cover-gray-plain'),
