(116, '1628110095.jpg', 'Cuddler Natural', 'Indulgently snuggly in mock lambswool!', 1, '1', '<p>Snooza Australian Made Cuddler is stunning to look at! But, it\'s what\'s inside that makes it unique. Finished in cosy soft natural mock lambswool both the cushion &amp; the outer ring have removable, washable covers AND separate zippered, washable inners. Zippered access to the Snoozafill® means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your machine. The base is covered in non-slip paws in case of over-excited running leaps to bed.</p>', '1', '1', '1628110121.jpg', '1628110135.jpg', '1628110151.jpg', 'Small', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 99.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 02:48:15', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '300', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove covers before washing. We recommend closing all zips and making use of a laundry bag to protect the long fibres.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cover :</span>&nbsp;Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Filling :&nbsp;</span>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p><p>-Polyester Covers</p><p>-Filled with Snoozafill®*</p><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-11 05:25:28', 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'cuddler-natural'),
(117, '1628112305.jpg', 'Snuggler Oslo NEW', 'NEW Updated Luxe Fabric Exterior!', 1, '1', '<p>The exterior fabric of our Australian Made Snuggler Oslo has been given a stunning update! The NEW Oslo features soft brushed furniture-grade velvet-like fabric in light grey with blue tones. The NEW Oslo replaces our previous Oslo/Grey Pewter exterior!</p>\r\n<p>Light grey plush lines the entire interior of the bed and helps to have a calming effect on your pet. Super comfort orthopaedic support foam cushions the base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered sides add protection and comfort providing a sense of calm for anxious pets.</p>\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '2', '1628112393.jpg', '1628112414.jpg', '1628112451.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, 159.9, 189.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 03:25:05', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '450', '350', '650', '550', NULL, '630', '410', '950', '680', NULL, '910', '560', '1150', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Base</span></p><p>Spot clean</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion (with fill)</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<ul><li>Polyester cover</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Snoozafill* side bolsters</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Faux fur plush interior lining</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</li></ul>\r\n<p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-30 00:58:32', 100, 100, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'snuggler-oslo-new'),
(118, '1628112667.jpg', 'Snooza Tuff Ortho Snuggler Indigo', '1650 Denier High-Density Performance Fabric Surround!', 1, '1', '<p>Our all-new Australian Made Snooza TUFF Snuggler has an extremely strong and durable exterior and reversible mat base. The 1650 Denier fabric is abrasion and scratch proof with a high performance, fade-resistant and waterproof exterior to handle Aussie conditions. The soft bolstered walls and one side of the reversible mat is lined with cosy plush Chinchilla faux fur while super comfort orthopaedic support foam cushions the base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The orthopaedic reversible and removable base has the option of chinchilla plush on one side and Tuff 1650 denier fabric on the other, handling muddy paws with ease. A breeze to keep clean the SnoozaTUFF exterior and water-resistant side of the mat can be wiped down easily and is also machine washable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable</p>', '1', '2', '1628112932.jpg', '1628112978.jpg', '1628112994.jpg', 'Medium', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 199.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 03:31:07', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '450', '350', '650', '550', NULL, '630', '410', '950', '680', NULL, '910', '560', '1150', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Base</span></p><p>Spot clean</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.<