(119, '1628113294.jpg', 'Snuggler Chinchilla', 'Now with super comfort orthopaedic foam and plush-lined interior!', 1, '1', '<p>Our new Australian Made Snuggler Chinchilla adds a touch of luxe to the modern home. Finished in upholstery grade two-tone fabric and dark grey toned plush faux fur that lines the entire interior of the bed. Super comfort orthopaedic support foam cushions the base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered sides add protection and comfort to calm your pet.</p>\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '2', '1628113327.jpg', '1628113346.jpg', '1628113355.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, 159.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 03:41:34', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '450', '350', '650', '550', NULL, '630', '410', '950', '680', NULL, '910', '560', '1150', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Base</span></p><p>Spot clean</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion (with fill)</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<ul><li>Polyester cover</li></ul><ul><li>Snoozafill* side bolsters</li></ul><ul><li>Faux fur plush interior lining</li></ul><ul><li>Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</li></ul><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>\r\n<p></p>', '2021-10-30 00:57:15', 100, 100, 100, NULL, NULL, 'snuggler-chinchilla'),
(120, '1628113603.jpg', 'Snuggler Pink', 'Limited Edition Pink Velvet!', 1, '1', '<p>Our New Limited Edition Pink Ortho Snuggler features soft luxurious furniture-grade velvet fabric in Pink</p>\r\n<p>Light grey plush lines the entire interior of the bed and helps to have a calming effect on your pet. Super comfort orthopaedic support foam cushions the base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered sides add protection and comfort providing a sense of calm for anxious pets.</p>\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '2', '1628113670.jpg', '1628113693.jpg', '1628113704.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, 159.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 03:46:43', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '450', '350', '650', '550', NULL, '630', '410', '950', '680', NULL, '910', '560', '1150', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p>\r\n<p><b>Foam Base</b></p>\r\n<p>Spot clean</p>\r\n<p><b>Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</b></p>\r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><b>Cushion (with fill)</b></p>\r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<ul><li>Polyester cover</li></ul><ul><li>Snoozafill* side bolsters</li></ul><ul><li>Faux fur plush interior lining</li></ul><ul><li>Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</li></ul><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>\r\n<p></p>', '2021-10-30 00:56:41', 500, 500, 500, NULL, NULL, 'snuggler-pink'),
(121, '1628114236.jpg', 'Ortho Sofa Chinchilla', 'Soft bolstered high walls, Australian Orthopaedic foam and a charchoal plush-lined interior!', 1, '1', '<p>Our new Australian Made Chinchilla Ortho Sofa features a super comfort orthopaedic support foam base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered walls add protection and comfort providing a sense of calm for anxious pets. The wide-open front provides easy access for pets allowing them to get on and off with ease. </p>\r\n<p>The Ortho Sofa is finished in upholstrey grade furnishing fabric and a super cosy dense pile charcoal plush that lines the entire interior of the bed and features zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '3', '1628114328.jpg', '1628114354.jpg', '1628114378.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 179.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 03:57:16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2021-08-05 03:59:38', 500, 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ortho-sofa-chinchilla'),
(122, '1628114595.jpg', 'Ortho Sofa Soho', 'Soft bolstered high walls, Australian orthopaedic foam & a plush-lined interior!', 1, '1', '<p>Our new luxurious Australian Made Ortho Sofa features a super comfort orthopaedic support foam base providing the perfect stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered walls add protection and comfort providing a sense of calm for anxious pets. The wide-open front provides easy access for pets allowing them to get on and off with ease. </p>\r\n<p>The Ortho Sofa is finished in furniture-grade two-tone fabric and a light grey plush that lines the entire interior of the bed and features zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable.</p>', '1', '3', '1628114642.jpg', '1628114680.jpg', '1628114692.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 179.9, 179.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 04:03:15', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2021-08-05 04:04:52', 500, 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ortho-sofa-soho'),
(123, '1628141999.jpg', 'Shapes Oblong Chinchilla', 'Gorgeously soft charcoal plush top paired with grey two-tone fabric!', 1, '1', '<p>Our Chinchilla Shapes Oblong Bed adds a touch of luxe to the modern home. Finished beautifully in two-tone grey upholstery grade fabric with self-piping and a dark grey plush faux fur top these gorgeously soft cushions will provide hours of indulgent snoozing for the most discerning pet.</p>\r\n<p>Features a zippered cover and replaceable, refillable and washable Snoozafill® insert.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>', '1', '10', '1628142131.jpg', '1628142196.jpg', '1628142211.jpg', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 169.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 11:39:59', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>', 'Length', 'Width', 'Height', NULL, NULL, 'Small', '750', '550', '70', NULL, NULL, '--', '--', '--', NULL, NULL, '1150', '750', '70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover before washing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Cover : </strong>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inner (fill) : </strong>\r\nWarm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.\r\n\r\nSnooza beds perform best when aired regularly.</p>', '<p>- Polyester Cover</p>\r\n<p>- Filled with Snoozafill®*</p>\r\n<p>*Our Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>', '2021-08-05 11:52:39', 500, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'shapes-oblong-chinchilla'),
(124, '1628143948.jpg', 'Chaise Lounge Smoke', 'Lowered front for easy entry & removable cover.', 1, '1', '<p>Our new Chaise Lounge in Smoke is finished in upholstery grade brushed herringbone fabric and self-piping. The channelled base consists of 3 separate inserts filled with Snoozafill to provide a cosy but stable base for younger and older dogs alike, while the soft filled bolstered sides add protection and comfort to calm your pet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '6', '1628144330.jpg', '1628144348.jpg', '1628144386.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 169.9, 249.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 12:12:28', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '550', '420', '850', '650', NULL, '780', '640', '1090', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and base inserts before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters &amp; Inserts</strong></p> \r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cushion (with fill)</strong></p> \r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p> - Polyester cover</p>\r\n<p> - Snoozafill* side bolsters &amp; base inserts</p>\r\n<p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium A