(127, '1628156217.jpg', 'Ortho Sofa Cover Soho', 'Change your cover, change your look!', 7, '40', '<p><strong>Ortho Sofa Replacement Cover Soho</strong></p> \r\n<p>Ortho Sofa Replacement cover in Soho features grey furniture grade two-tone fabric and a light grey plush faux fur that lines the entire interior of the bed. Fully zippered for easy washing. </p>\r\n<p>The large wrap-around bolster has its own compartment for easy assembly/disassembly while the orthopaedic foam mattress has its own separate compartment too. Non-slip paws on the base complete the design.</p>', '84', '58', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 107.95, 131.95, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 15:36:57', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Base</span></p><p>Spot clean</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion (with fill)</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>- *Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p><p>- Polyester cover</p><p>- Snoozafill* side bolsters</p><p>- Faux fur plush interior lining</p><p>- Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</p><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p><p><br></p>', '2021-10-08 19:07:09', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'ortho-sofa-cover-soho'),
(128, '1628156455.jpg', 'Ortho Sofa Cover Chinchilla', 'Change your cover, change your look!', 7, '40', '<p><strong>Ortho Sofa Replacement Cover Chinchilla</strong></p> \r\n<p> Ortho Sofa Replacement cover in Chinchilla features dark grey upholstery grade two-tone fabric and charcoal grey toned plush faux fur that lines the entire interior of the bed (fur tone may vary due to two-stage dying process). Fully zippered for easy washing. </p>\r\n<p>The large wrap-around bolster has its own compartment for easy assembly/disassembly while the orthopaedic foam mattress has its own separate compartment too. Non-slip paws on the base complete the design.</p>', '84', '58', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 107.95, 131.95, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 15:40:55', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '500', '920', '700', NULL, '780', '600', '1200', '800', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Foam Base</strong></p> \r\n<p>Spot clean</p>\r\n<p><strong>Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</strong></p> \r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cushion (with fill)</strong></p>\r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p> - *Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<p> - Polyester cover</p>\r\n<p> - Snoozafill* side bolsters</p>\r\n<p> - Faux fur plush interior lining</p>\r\n<p> 