(129, '1628157342.jpg', 'Buddy Bed Cover Set NEW Oslo', 'Includes Oslo Body Cover & Cushion Cover', 7, '40', '<p><strong>Buddy Bed Cover Set - NEW Oslo</strong></p> \r\n<p>The replacement body cover &amp; cushion cover set for our Soothing &amp; Calming Buddy Bed in luxurious NEW Oslo colourway.  Give your older Buddy a new lease on with this luxurious set.</p>\r\n<p>Body cover and cushion cover are not available for purchase separately.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '84', '59', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, 59.95, 79.95, 101.95, 125.95, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-05 15:55:42', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '530', '500', NULL, NULL, NULL, '640', '600', NULL, NULL, NULL, '800', '720', NULL, NULL, NULL, '980', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover before washing. Warm machine wash 40°C.</p><p>Cool tumble dry.</p><p>We recommend washing separately, closing all zips and using a laundry bag to prevent damage in the wash.</p>', '<p>- Polyester Cover</p><p><br></p>', '2021-10-08 19:08:47', 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, 'buddy-bed-cover-set-new-oslo'),
