(149, '1628331574.jpg', 'Snooza TUFF Pro Mattress Cover Red', 'High-Density Nylon Fabric - Tough & Water-Resistant', 7, '40', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Snooza TUFF Pro Mattress Cover Red</span></p><p>The replacement cover for our Snooza TUFF Mattress Pro is built extremely strong and durable and crafted for all conditions. Ideal for outdoor, and made from Black nylon fabric the TUFF Pro Mattress cover is UV treated, fade-resistant and water-repellent. The cover is easily removable, washable and replaceable.</p>', '84', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, NULL, 75.99, 89.99, 129.99, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-07 16:19:34', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p>Remove cover before washing</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong></p> \r\n<p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Inserts (with fill)</strong></p> \r\n<p>This bed is not only super tough it also has a water repellent cover. This means that dogs &amp; water will have a hard time getting in but it also means it\'s difficult for air to get out. The cover does feature 4 small holes (2 in each back corner) for breathability and to let air escape, however, it\'s important to take the cover off and air the inner regularly to ensure it stays in tip-top condition.</p>\r\n<p>Trapped air can also mean it may take a little more time for your dog to get used to how this bed feels. But be patient the \'puffiness\' will subside.</p>', '<p>This bed is tough but not indestructible, please beware of four-legged motivated repeat offenders.</p><p>- 1000 Denier Nylon Cover</p>', '2021-08-07 16:25:26', 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, 'snooza-tuff-pro-mattress-cover-red'),
