(192, '1628850991.jpg', 'Flea-Free Dog Bed Green', 'Powdercoated steel frame with a durable mesh cover!', 1, '1', '<p><strong>Flea-Free Dog Bed</strong></p> \r\n<p>Australian made here by us and built to last, we cut and bend square 19mm &amp; 25.4mm steel tube before powdercoating the steel frame with a high gloss heritage green finish. Our tough, open-weave, breathable outdoor fabric cover is a cinch to clean (just wipe down) &amp; with a four bolt assembly it\'s simple to replace.</p>\r\n<p>Raised approximately 20cm off the ground to ensure cold air flows under rather than through your pet. The Flea-Free is the most versatile of Snooza raised beds as it can take any covers &amp; accessories... Original, Fleaproofer, Woolly Cover, Multimat. We also ensure you can always get replacement parts, right down to the bolts.</p>\r\n<p>The Flatpack Flea-Free: If you\'re ordering your Flea-Free online it will come in flatpack form. Which will mean assembly is required.</p>', '2', '29', '1628851010.jpg', '1628851021.jpg', '1628851031.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, 99.9, 109.9, 125.9, 139.9, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-13 16:36:31', 'Sleeping area. All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes are approximate. For overall length of the bed (including the legs) add approximately 20cm.</p>', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '690', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '900', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1020', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1150', '780', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove the cover. Wash with a mix of 1/4 cup bleach, 1/4 cup of mild detergent &amp; 4 litres of water. Do not use solvent based cleaners. Line dry only.<br></p>', '<p>Synthetic Cover</p>\r\n<p>Australian Steel</p>', '2021-10-18 14:56:21', 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, 'flea-free-dog-bed-green'),
(193, '1628851587.jpg', 'Original Snooza Dog Bed', 'Galvanised steel frame with a handstitched cover - no staples!', 1, '1', '<p><strong>The Original Snooza Dog Bed - since 1989</strong></p> \r\n<p>Made to withstand the harshest conditions, this is the bed that started us in 1989! Australian made here by us, we use 25.4mm steel tube galvanised on both sides (so that it won\'t rust from the inside out), we weld the frame at all contact points &amp; then hand sew (we will never use staples) a new durable jute cover on it.</p>', '2', '30', '1628851627.jpg', '1628851636.jpg', NULL, 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, 94.9, 99.9, 109.9, 119.9, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-13 16:46:27', 'Sleeping area. All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes are approximate. For overall length of the bed (including the legs) add approximately 20cm.</p>', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '690', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '900', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1020', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1150', '780', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove dirt with a stiff brush.</p>\r\n<p>Hose down.</p>\r\n<p>Allow to dry in Sun</p>\r\n<p>Ensure mat is completely dry before reassembly.</p>', '<p> - Jute Cover</p>\r\n<p> - Australian Steel</p>', '2021-10-18 14:29:02', 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, 'original-snooza-dog-bed'),
(194, '1628854355.jpg', 'Fleaproofer Dog Bed - Black', 'Australian made galvanised steel frame with a durable cover!', 1, '1', '<p><strong>Fleaproofer Dog Bed - Black</strong></p> \r\n<p>Australian made by us, the Fleaproofer sits 20cm above the ground and features the Snooza Original Dog Bed frame with a shade cloth type cover that the fleas will just hate to live in! With 2 velcro tabs to hold it in place &amp; ultra high-tech UV treated thread &amp; fabric, the cover is perfect for outdoor conditions. Made to suit those customers who had an Original Dog Bed but wanted a \'Flea-Free\' style cover - now you can.</p>\r\n<p>Snooza Fleaproofer frame can also be used withour Original Dog Bed covers as well as our many accessories - Woolly Covers, Multimats...</p>', '2', '31', '1628854450.jpg', '1628854460.jpg', '1628854476.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, 88.9, 99.9, 109.99, 129.9, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-08-13 17:32:35', 'Sleeping area. All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '690', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '900', '550', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1020', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '1150', '750', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove the cover. Wash with a mix of 1/4 cup bleach, 1/4 cup of mild detergent &amp; 4 litres of water. Do not use solvent based cleaners. Line dry only.</p>', '<p> - Synthetic Cover</p>\r\n<p> - Australian Steel</p>', '2021-10-18 14:26:46', 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, 'fleaproofer-dog-bed-black'),
(198, '1633428275.jpg', 'Skin & Coat Care Wipes - Unbleached', 'Made from compostable bamboo fibre', 8, '9', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Skin &amp; Coat Care Wipes</span></p><p>Gentle on your pet, and our planet</p><p>Unbleached, compostable &amp; biodegradable dog care wipes.</p><p>Gentle on your pet and gentle on our planet, they are made from 100% bamboo &amp; enriched with aloe vera, vitamin E &amp; baking soda to absorb odours.</p><p>Snooza\'s skin &amp; coat wipes are a caring, handy addition to your daily pet cleaning routine, suitable for all dog breeds at any age.</p><p>The hypoallergenic formula is mild enough to use every day on all areas - paws, face and under the tail! Our wipes are made of sustainable bamboo and can be disposed of in your compost bin, where they will break down without harming the environment. Made from all-natural ingredients. Chemical &amp; toxin-free. Do not flush</p>', '83', '82', '1633428323.jpg', '1633428329.jpg', '1633428335.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 14.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-05 16:04:35', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, '<p>100% compostable bamboo fibre</p>\r\n<p>80 per pack!</p>', '2021-10-29 22:07:44', NULL, NULL, 1000, NULL, NULL, 'skin-and-coat-care-wipes-unbleached'),
(199, '1633688553.jpg', 'The Cat Bed Leopard', 'Convertible & reversible - use 3 ways!', 2, '44', '<p><strong>The Cat Bed Leopard</strong></p> \r\n<p>Designed for the quarantine services of Australia for use in their feline facility. The brief was big… with washability (for obvious reasons) &amp; durability being most important of all. The Cat Bed is a favourite, as it can be inverted, reversed &amp; converted &amp; is fully machine washable &amp; extra durable. It’s made using luxurious leopard print faux fur and dependable, soft polar fleece. The opening has flexible boning to keep it open or rolled down as you please. Use this bed in its tunnel form with the plush fur inside or out, rolled into a pod or turn it into a cuddly round bed. This ultimate cat bed is also great for small dogs, rabbits, guinea pigs, ferrets &amp; rats. This cat bed is also covered by the Snooza Repair Service.</p>', '116', '42', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 69.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-08 16:22:33', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-16 19:37:31', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'the-cat-bed-leopard'),
(200, '1633692227.jpg', 'Cat Scratching Pole Base', 'Every piece of our cat pole is replaceable!', 2, '52', '<p><strong>Cat Scratching Pole Base</strong></p> \r\n<p>The great thing about our cat scratching poles is you can replace the base if your cat likes to scratch this too. Simply screw the old one off and screw the new one on!</p>\r\n<p>You can also replace the entire pole if you need to and we sell covers separately!</p>', '15', '53', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 24.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-08 17:23:47', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '0', '0', '0', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cover</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Base</span></p><p>Sponge clean only.</p>', '<ul><li><b>-Polyester Cover</b></li></ul><p><b><br></b></p>', '2021-10-16 19:39:38', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'cat-scratching-pole-base'),
(201, '1633907209.jpg', 'Cuddler Dune', 'Provides comfort & security for anxious pets!', 1, '1', '<p><strong>Soothing &amp; Calming Cuddler in Dune</strong></p> \r\n<p>Snooza Australian Made Cuddler in luxurious Dune is the perfect bed to calm and relax your pet. Super soft long pile vegan faux fur paired with soft raised walls and a deep sleeping area provide the ultimate retreat for anxious pets and those that relish the feeling of safety and security. The Dune Cuddler invites hours of delicious snoozing and is fully machine washable (even the filling!).</p>\r\n<p>Features removable, replaceable and washable covers on both the outer ring and cushion. Filled with Snoozafill, our Australian Foam and recycled PET fibre mix, zippered access to the inner liners means you can top up your filling if you ever need to or make use of our Laundry Bag if your complete Cuddler doesn\'t fit your washing machine.</p>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>', '1', '1', '1633907314.jpg', '1633907328.jpg', '1633907368.jpg', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', NULL, NULL, 119.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-11 05:06:49', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>', 'Diameter of sleeping area', 'Diameter of outside edge', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '450', '700', NULL, NULL, NULL, '600', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, '700', '1100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', 'true', NULL, '<p>Remove covers before washing. We recommend closing all zips and making use of a laundry bag to protect the long fibres.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cover :</span>&nbsp;Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Filling :&nbsp;</span>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p><p>-Polyester Covers</p><p>-Filled with Snoozafill®*</p><p>*Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>', '2021-10-18 14:08:33', 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, 'cuddler-dune'),
(202, '1633909121.jpg', 'Calming Multimat Chinchilla', 'Fully washable go-anywhere mat; perfect for crate, floor, car & home.', 1, '1', '<p><strong>Multimat Chinchilla</strong></p> \r\n<p>Snooza Australian Made Chinchilla Mulitmat® is the perfect all-round versatile Mat. The Multimat® is a fantastic go-anywhere multi-purpose mat, our dogs use it just about anywhere - it makes a super floor mat, crate mat, puppy training mat, in the car or on holiday. Made in Melbourne, thick wadding is encased in charcoal plush faux fur and then notched to keep it in place. We\'ve added velcro tabs at each corner to fit all Snooza Raised Bed (to stop it sliding around), and because it\'s a \'ridgy-didge\' Australian Made Snooza Multimat® it is fully machine washable.</p>\r\n<p>If you\'re looking to use your Chinchilla Multimat on one of our raised beds, the sizes are one size down i.e. a medium size Multimat will fit a Small size Original Dog Bed, Fleaproofer or Flea-Free Dog Bed, a large-size Multimat will fit a medium raised bed etc</p>\r\n<p>Please note: our Choc/Sand Polar Fleece Multimat &amp; Chinchilla Multimat both have differences in sizing. The Chinchilla Multimat is designed to fit the most popular crate sizes as well as our raised beds.</p>', '1', '69', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', 'Extra - Large', 'XXL', 69.9, 79.9, 89.9, 99.9, 109.9, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-11 05:38:41', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '2021-10-16 19:35:34', 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 'calming-multimat-chinchilla'),
(203, '1633911356.jpg', 'Organic Pet Futon Ash Grey', 'Warm in winter, cool in summer ~ our Pet Futon now comes in Organic Cotton!', 1, '1', '<p><strong>Organic Cotton Pet Futon\r\n</strong></p><p><strong><br></strong>The Organic Cotton Pet Futon features a white print on an ash grey organic cover. Offering the ultimate in versatility &amp; comfort for your pet, wool has always been recognised as the ideal fibre for bedding. It provides natural breathability and temperature regulation, so it\'s warm in winter cool in summer.</p> \r\n<p>Now with extra comfort. Inside an anti-allergy organic cotton casing, we put Australian wool blended with predominantly recycled PET to ensure it\'s a breeze to keep clean (it\'s machine washable &amp; dry cleanable!). We close the cover, quilt the Futon to keep the filling in place &amp; then encase it with a removable, ash grey coloured washable organic cotton cover. Ideal for the car, weekends away, in the kennel or even on one of our raised beds! </p>', '1', '71', '1633912041.jpg', '1633911696.jpg', '1633912051.jpg', 'MINI', 'ORIGINAL', 'MIGHTY', NULL, NULL, 79.9, 89.9, 109.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-11 06:15:56', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<div><br></div>', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '520', '420', NULL, NULL, NULL, '830', '530', NULL, NULL, NULL, '980', '680', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove cover before washing</p>\r\n<p>As this product contains wool &amp; organic cotton, much like your own bedding, it’s important to air it out regularly. This is particularly important during winter or damp weather as wool naturally draws &amp; stores moisture from the surrounding air.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cover</strong></p> \r\n<p>Gentle machine wash 30c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Warm iron. Do not dry clean.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Inner (wool blend mattress) </strong></p> \r\n<p>Gentle machine wash on a wool cycle only. Cool tumble dry or line dry. Air in the sun regularly. </p>', '<ul><li>Australian Wool Blend Batt</li><li>Organic Cotton</li></ul>', '2021-10-18 14:07:52', 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, 'organic-pet-futon-ash-grey'),
