(206, '1633918922.jpg', 'Doo Doo Good Eco Bags', '100% compostable. Doo Doo Good for our community and our planet.', 8, '9', '<p>Doo Good for our community and for our planet.\r\nSnooza Doo Doo Good Eco Bags are made from 100% compostable, planet-friendly corn starch &amp; plant-based materials, leaving no microplastics behind. Not only are they planet friendly, but people-friendly too!</p>\r\n<p>The bags are soft to touch and easy to separate, made from corn starch and plant-based materials</p>\r\n<p>They are made to fit the Doo Doo Good Eco Bag Dispenser which are made from Snooza bed off-cuts and help to reduce waste. Once used, dispose of the waste bags into your home compost or regular rubbish bin.</p>\r\n<p>Contact your council for suitable composting locations, or build your own DIY doo doo composting unit.</p>\r\n<p>*Bag dispenser not included</p>', '10', NULL, '1633919209.jpg', '1633919220.jpg', '1633919226.jpg', '60PK', '180PK', NULL, NULL, NULL, 14.9, 29.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-11 08:22:02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, '<ul><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Made from corn starch &amp; plant-based materials</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">18 micron, plastic-free soft-touch material</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Fully biodegradable</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Certified by the&nbsp;Australiasian Biodegradable Association</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Meets Australian, European &amp; USA compostable standards</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 22:23:30', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'doo-doo-good-eco-bags'),
(207, '1633919522.jpg', 'Doo Doo Good Eco Bag Dispenser Black', 'Reusing fabric & reducing our waste. Made to dispense Doo Doo Good Eco Bags', 8, '9', '<p>This Doo Doo Good Eco Bag dispenser wraps securely around your lead and ensures your waste bags come along for every walk, with an easy-action system allowing you to pull out the waste bags one at a time, quickly and easily. These dispensers are planet friendly- they help reduce waste by re-using fabric from Snooza bed off-cuts!</p>\r\n<p>But they are more than just planet-friendly - they are people-friendly too. With every purchase, we donate 50% of the profit to Animal Assistance charities. These very special dogs and cats provide support and companionship for many who suffer from PTSD, Autism, Diabetes and Anxiety. They also assist in aged care homes, schools, with the mobility impaired and other special needs</p>\r\n<p>*Made to fit <a href=\"https://mypuppymypet.demo-meritzeal2.com/product-details/206%22\" target=\"_blank\">Doo Doo Good Eco Bags</a>. Bags sold separately.</p>', '10', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 14.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-11 08:32:02', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, '<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 1.2rem; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">100% tough polyester &amp; nylon fabric off-cuts</p><ul data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Poppins, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Black - high-density nylon</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Navy - high-density polyester</li><li data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\">Grey - water-proof polyester<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">- Due to the nature of supply, colour and fabric of dispenser can vary</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 22:20:28', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'doo-doo-good-eco-bag-dispenser-black'),
(208, '1635568818.jpg', 'Marble Bowl Grey', 'Luxurious natural marble pet bowl', 8, '16', '<p>These stunning contemporary style pet bowls are made from natural marble stone and thoughtfully designed to be practical and to complement a modern home. They have a chemical-free natural surface that is safe for your pet and is entirely BPA free &amp; plastic-free.</p><p>Natural stone is also great for keeping your pet’s water cool and is well-weighted with 10mm thick sturdy walls to prevent tripping and slipping. They\'re suitable for both food and water and are easy to wash with just warm soapy water. Available in two stunning colours - Light Grey &amp; Dark Charcoal - you can mix and match the colours and sizes to suit your pet and your home. Marble is a natural stone and colours and patterns will vary slightly from photography.</p>', '131', '79', '1635568800.jpg', '1635567489.jpg', '1635567498.jpg', 'Small', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 79.9, 99.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 19:24:54', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Diameter', 'Height', 'Depth', NULL, NULL, 'Small', '170', '70', '50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '210', '90', '70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Avoid abrasive or oil-based cleaners.</li></ul><ul><li>Dishwasher proof but stone can absorb chemicals from dishwashing powder.</li></ul><ul><li>Marble is a natural stone. Colours and patterns will vary from photography.</li><li>We recommend hand washing with warm soapy water.</li></ul><ul><li>Any surface stains can be removed with a paste made from baking powder and warm water, gently scrub the internal surface.</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Genuine marble stone</li><li>BPA free</li><li>Plastic-free</li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Chemical-free</span></li></ul>', '2021-10-29 20:40:19', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'marble-bowl-grey'),
