le-bowl-charcoal'),
(210, '1635569398.jpg', 'Double Wall Stainless Steel Bowl Slate Grey', 'Durable, food-grade, non-slip pet bowls', 8, '16', '<p>The Double Wall Stainless Steel bowls are made extra tough, so you can use them either indoors or outdoors. We\'ve used high quality and modern materials - double stainless steel walls, and protective powder coating finish- to make these bowls durable, and rust, chip and fade resistant. They are heavy and sturdy, which helps to prevent tipping over, with non-slip rubber on the base so there is no slipping around while your pet is trying to enjoy their meal! Made from food-grade stainless steel, free from chemicals and BPA, these bowls are safe and versatile- suitable for food or water, and perfect for raw, dry or moist food. Available in 1.25L or 2L, in Slate Grey or Salt White.<br></p>', '131', '81', '1635569389.jpg', '1635569414.jpg', NULL, 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 59.9, 79.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 20:47:08', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Height', 'Depth', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '180', '65', NULL, NULL, NULL, '200', '90', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Do not use abrasive cleaners or brushes</li><li>Wash before use with warm soapy water</li><li>Bowl can be placed in dishwasher</li></ul>', '<ul><li>304 Stainless Steel</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 20:53:51', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'double-wall-stainless-steel-bowl-slate-grey'),
(211, '1635569482.jpg', 'Double Wall Stainless Steel Bowl Salt White', 'Durable, food-grade, non-slip pet bowls', 8, '16', '<p>The Double Wall Stainless Steel bowls are made extra tough, so you can use them either indoors or outdoors. We\'ve used high quality and modern materials - double stainless steel walls, and protective powder coating finish- to make these bowls durable, and rust, chip and fade resistant. They are heavy and sturdy, which helps to prevent tipping over, with non-slip rubber on the base so there is no slipping around while your pet is trying to enjoy their meal! Made from food-grade stainless steel, free from chemicals and BPA, these bowls are safe and versatile- suitable for food or water, and perfect for raw, dry or moist food. Available in 1.25L or 2L, in Slate Grey or Salt White.<br></p>', '131', '81', '1635569508.jpg', '1635569518.jpg', NULL, 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, NULL, 59.9, 79.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 20:51:22', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Height', 'Depth', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '180', '65', NULL, NULL, NULL, '200', '90', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Do not use abrasive cleaners or brushes</li><li>Wash before use with warm soapy water</li><li>Bowl can be placed in dishwasher</li></ul>', '<ul><li>304 Stainless Steel</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 20:53:47', 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'double-wall-stainless-steel-bowl-salt-white'),
(212, '1635569810.jpg', 'Concrete & Stainless Steel Pet Bowl Sage Green', 'Contemporary style with matt finish & removable stainless steel inner bowl', 8, '16', '<p>These beautiful, matt-finished bowls have been thoughtfully designed to be both practical and modern. They are easy to fill and wash, with a removable stainless inner bowl, which is rust-proof, hygenic, BPA free and suitable for all food types including raw meat. The outer bowl is made from modern polyresin with a concrete finish, and features non-slip rubber trims, to prevent sliding while your pet enjoys their meal. The clever shape of this bowl ensures that the bowl tipping over is highly unlikely! We\'ve made two modern colours to complement any home interior.</p><p>Available in two colours - Sage Green &amp; Charcoal</p>', '131', '80', '1635569917.jpg', '1635569944.png', '1635569964.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 49.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 20:56:50', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Diameter', 'Height', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '200', '70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>We recommend hand washing with warm soapy water.</li><li>Avoid abrasive products on both inner and outer bowls.. Inner stainless steel bowl is dishwasher safe.</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Outer Bowl - Polyresin with Concrete Coating</li></ul><ul><li>Inner Bowl - Food Grade 304 Stainless Steel</li><li>Non-slip base to prevent slipping &amp; tipping</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 21:01:31', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'concrete-and-stainless-steel-pet-bowl-sage-green'),
(213, '1635569952.jpg', 'Concrete & Stainless Steel Pet Bowl Charcoal', 'Contemporary style with matt finish & removable stainless steel inner bowl', 8, '16', '<p>These beautiful, matt-finished bowls have been thoughtfully designed to be both practical and modern. They are easy to fill and wash, with a removable stainless inner bowl, which is rust-proof, hygenic, BPA free and suitable for all food types including raw meat. The outer bowl is made from modern polyresin with a concrete finish, and features non-slip rubber trims, to prevent sliding while your pet enjoys their meal. The clever shape of this bowl ensures that the bowl tipping over is highly unlikely! We\'ve made two modern colours to complement any home interior.</p><p>Available in two colours - Sage Green &amp; Charcoal</p>', '131', '80', '1635569902.jpg', '1635569916.jpg', '1635569930.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 49.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 20:57:32', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Diameter', 'Height', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '200', '70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>We recommend hand washing with warm soapy water.</li><li>Avoid abrasive products on both inner and outer bowls.. Inner stainless steel bowl is dishwasher safe.</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Outer Bowl - Polyresin with Concrete Coating</li></ul><ul><li>Inner Bowl - Food Grade 304 Stainless Steel</li><li>Non-slip base to prevent slipping &amp; tipping</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 21:01:31', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'concrete-and-stainless-steel-pet-bowl-charcoal'),
(214, '1635574293.jpg', 'Skin & Coat Care Wipes - White', NULL, 8, '9', '<p>Gentle on your pet, and our planet</p>\r\n<p>Made from 100% bamboo &amp; enriched with aloe vera, vitamin E &amp; baking soda to absorb odours.</p>\r\n<p>Snooza Wipes are a caring, handy addition to your daily pet cleaning routine, suitable for all dog breeds at any age.</p>\r\n<p>The hypoallergenic formula is mild enough to use every day on all areas - paws, face and under the tail! Our wipes are made of sustainable bamboo and can be disposed of in your compost bin, where they will break down without harming the environment.\r\nMade from all-natural ingredients. Chemical &amp; toxin-free</p>', '83', '82', '1635574430.jpg', '1635574439.jpg', '1635574449.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 14.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 22:11:33', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>100% compostable bamboo fibre</p><p>80 per pack!</p>', '2021-10-29 22:14:09', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'skin-and-coat-care-wipes-white'),
(215, '1635575744.jpg', 'Dry Luxe Blanket', 'Luxurious waterproof blanket for your sofa or pet\'s bed for protection from little accidents', 8, '9', '<p>This luxurious Dry Luxe Blanket uses 100% waterproof lining and the same calming plush fabric as our popular Calming Cuddler Chinchilla beds. The dark long-pile plush and the short, light-coloured pile will complement most modern furniture.\r\nThe blanket is designed to drape over your sofa, your bed or dog\'s bed, or in the car, keeping them protected from little accidents, while the calming, soft fabric keeps your dog warm and cosy. Perfect for puppies or senior dogs.\r\nMade with soft, furnishing grade, machine washable materials in a generous size - for small up to even larger dogs.\r\nFor measurements please see the size chart below.\r\n\r\n </p>', '132', '83', '1635575780.jpg', '1635575791.jpg', '1635575799.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 129.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 22:35:44', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '1500', '1000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Warm machine wash 40 degrees C</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Line dry is best but can be tumble-dried on low heat</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Do not iron</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Do not dry clean</li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Machine washable</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Do not bleach.</span></li></ul>', '<ul><li>100% waterproof lining made from TPU</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>100% polyester furnishing-grade plush fabric</li></ul>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '2021-10-29 22:40:59', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dry-luxe-blanket'),
(216, '1635576367.jpg', 'Calming Cuddler Blanket Sliver Fox', 'Designed to drape over your dog, keeping them warm, cuddled and comforted, or use as a calming cover for your bed, furniture or dog bed.', 8, '9', '<p>This calming and luxurious reversible Cuddler Blanket uses the same calming, long-pile plush as our popular Calming Cuddler Silver Fox &amp; Chinchilla beds, for soothing your pet and keeping them warm too.</p>\r\n<p>Designed to drape over your dog, keeping them warm, cuddled and comforted. Use as a calming cover to drape over your dog bed or sofa, or any other surface where your dog likes to rest.</p>\r\n<p>Made with soft furnishing grade materials with beautiful, long-pile plush in a generous size - for small, medium and even larger dogs. For measurements please see the size chart below.  </p>', '132', '83', '1635576474.jpg', '1635576608.jpg', '1635576598.jpg', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 89.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 22:46:07', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.<br></p>', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '1450', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Warm machine wash 40 degrees C</li></ul><ul><li>Line dry is best but can be tumble-dried on low heat</li></ul><ul><li>Do not iron</li></ul><ul><li>Do not dry clean</li></ul><ul><li>Machine washable</li><li>Do not bleach.</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Reversible double-sided plush in Silver Fox &amp; Chinchilla</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Furnishing grade fabric</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>100% polyester</li></ul>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '2021-10-29 23:00:24', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'calming-cuddler-blanket-silver-fox'),
(217, '1635576438.png', 'Calming Cuddler Blanket Mink', 'Designed to drape over your dog, keeping them warm, cuddled and comforted, or use as a calming cover for your bed, furniture or dog bed.', 8, '9', '<p>This calming and luxurious reversible Cuddler Blanket uses the same calming, long-pile plush as our popular Calming Cuddler Mink bed, for soothing your pet, giving them a cosy place to be no matter where you are, and keeps them warm in cooler weather too.</p>\r\n<p>Use as a calming cover to drape in their bed, over your bed or sofa, in the car, or any other place where your dog likes to rest. Made with soft furnishing grade materials with beautiful, long-pile plush in a generous size - for small, medium and even larger dogs. For measurements please see the size chart below.</p>', '132', '83', '1635576481.jpg', '1635576574.jpg', '1635576589.png', 'OS', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8.9, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-29 22:47:18', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', '<p>All sizes have been measured to the best of our ability. But when dealing with soft things, we can only approximate.</p>', 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'One Size', '1450', '900', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<ul><li>Warm machine wash 40 degrees C</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Line dry is best but can be tumble-dried on low heat</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Do not iron</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Do not dry clean</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Machine washable</li><li>Do not bleach.</li></ul>', '<ul><li>Reversible double-sided plush in Mink</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Furnishing grade fabric</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>100% polyester</li></ul>\r\n<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur.</p>', '2021-10-29 22:58:53', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'calming-cuddler-blanket-mink'),
(218, '1635577590.jpg', 'Organic Pet Futon Charcoal', 'Warm in winter, cool in summer ~ our Pet Futon now comes in Organic Cotton!', 1, '1', '<p>Snooza’s iconic organic cotton cover &amp; wool inner Pet Futon now comes in contemporary charcoal. Offering the ultimate in versatility &amp; comfort for your pet, wool has always been recognised as the ideal fibre for bedding. It provides natural breathability and temperature regulation, so it\'s warm in winter cool in summer. </p>\r\n<p>Inside an anti-allergy organic cotton casing, we put an Australian wool insert blended with predominantly recycled PET to ensure it\'s a breeze to keep clean (it\'s machine washable &amp; dry cleanable). We close the cover, quilt the Futon to keep the filling in place &amp; then encase it with a removable, washable organic cotton cover. Ideal for the car, weekends away, and they also fit our raised beds such as the Flea-Free Raised Bed.</p>', '1', '71', '1635577676.jpg', '1635577684.jpg', '1635577717.jpg', 'MINI', 'ORIGINAL', 'MIGHTY', NULL, NULL, 79.9, 99.9, 109.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Out of Stock', 'Out of Stock', '2021-10-29 23:06:30', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length', 'Width', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Small', '520', '420', NULL, NULL, NULL, '830', '530', NULL, NULL, NULL, '980', '680', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove cover before washing</p><p>As this product contains wool &amp; organic cotton, much like your own bedding, it’s important to air it out regularly. This is particularly important during winter or damp weather as wool naturally draws &amp; stores moisture from the surrounding air.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cover</span></p><p>Gentle machine wash 30c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Warm iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Inner (wool blend mattress)</span></p><p>Gentle machine wash on a wool cycle only. Cool tumble dry or line dry. Air in the sun regularly.</p>', '<ul><li>Australian Wool Blend Batt</li><li>Organic Cotton</li></ul>', '2021-10-29 23:13:17', 1000, 1000, 1000, 0, 0, 'organic-pet-futon-charcoal'),
(219, '1635582894.jpg', 'Calming Snuggler Silver Fox', 'Perfect for pets with anxiety and an orthopaedic base as well', 1, '1', '<p>Snooza  new Australian Made Calming Snuggler in Silver Fox features the same long pile fur as our calming cuddlers but with the structure and support of soft filled bolstered walls and a super comfort orthopaedic support base. Perfect for younger and older dogs alike but with that added support that may benefit some pets more. The soft filled bolstered sides and sensory long pile faux fur will help foster the feeling of protection and comfort to calm your pet.</p>\r\n<p>Features a non-slip base and zippered removable covers for easy washing. Each bolster is removable, replaceable and of course washable. </p>', '1', '2', '1635582924.jpg', '1635582934.jpg', '1635582942.jpg', 'Small', 'Medium', 'Large', NULL, NULL, 159.9, 189.9, 229.9, NULL, NULL, 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', 'Available', '2021-10-30 00:34:54', 'All measurements are in millimetres (mm)', NULL, 'Length of sleeping area', 'Width of sleeping area', 'Length to the outside edge', 'Width of outside edge', NULL, 'Small', '450', '350', '650', '550', NULL, '630', '410', '950', '680', NULL, '910', '560', '1150', '850', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'true', 'true', NULL, NULL, '<p>Remove body cover, bolsters and foam base before washing.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Foam Base</span></p><p>Spot clean</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Covers &amp; Soft Filled Bolsters</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Cushion (with fill)</span></p><p>Warm machine wash 40c. Do not bleach. Cool tumble dry. Do not iron. Do not dry clean.</p>', '<p>*Please note: Due to the nature of the two-stage dyeing process, some shade/colour variations and markings may occur. </p>\r\n<ul><li>Polyester Faux Fur Cover</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Snoozafill* side bolsters</li></ul>\r\n<ul><li>Australian Made Super Comfort Orthopaedic Foam</li></ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">*</span>Snoozafill is a special blend of recycled PET fibre (made from plastic drinking bottles) and premium Australian made foam specifically designed for pets. Perfect for pets and friendly to the planet.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>', '2021-10-30 00:51:01', 1000, 1000, 1000, NULL, NULL, 'calming-snuggler-silver-fox');
